# This crate is OPT-IN and built only via its own manifest for LOCAL validation
# against a sibling working copy (path deps). Its Cargo.lock is therefore an
# environment-specific artifact (it pins whatever sibling versions the local
# validation used) and is intentionally NOT committed — CI integration will use
# git deps + a lead-resolved version scheme (see the WP-#97 report / ADR-0017
# follow-up). Regenerate locally with:
#   cargo build --manifest-path crates/lightr-cri-serve/Cargo.toml
/Cargo.lock
